.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-SNAPSHOT 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-snapshot \- export and review Grafana snapshot inventory bundles
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util snapshot [\fISUBCOMMAND\fR] [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
export and review Grafana snapshot inventory bundles.
.PP
when you want a local snapshot root that captures dashboard and datasource inventory for later inspection.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B export
export dashboard and datasource inventory into a local snapshot bundle. Use when: Need a local snapshot root that can be reviewed without Grafana access.
.TP
.B review
review a local snapshot inventory without touching Grafana. Use when: Want to inspect an exported snapshot root as table, csv, text, json, yaml, or interactive output.
